
'''Anne-Marie Goumba''' (wavutse ku ya 9 Ukwakira 1954), ni umwe mu bagize Inteko ishinga amategeko ya [[Repubulika ya Santara Afurika|Repubulika ya Centrafrique]] kandi ni umwe mu bagize Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Pan-Afurika kuva [[Repubulika ya Santara Afurika|muri Repubulika ya Centrafrique]] . Ni umupfakazi wuwahoze ari umunyapolitiki muri [[Repubulika ya Santara Afurika|Repubulika ya Centrafrique]] Abel Goumba <ref>https://peoplepill.com/people/anne-marie-goumba/lists</ref><ref>https://m.famousfix.com/list/women-members-of-the-pan-african-parliament</ref>.

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Anne-Marie Mbakondo yavutse ku ya 9 Ukwakira 1954 i [[Akarere ka Nyanza|Nyanza]], mu [[Rwanda]] . Yabanje kwiga amashuri makuru muri École Normale Supérieure i Save, mu [[Rwanda]], mbere yo gukomeza kwiga muri Université Catholique d'Afrique Centrale . Nyuma yaje gukora umurimo wo kwigisha nka mwarimu mu ishami ry’ubuvuzi rya [[Butare]] hagati ya 1973 na 1977. Agezeyo, yahuye na Abel Goumba, na we wari umwarimu ku bibazo by'ubuzima rusange, nyuma amugira umugore. <ref name="dictionary">https://books.google.com/books?id=aSxIDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA313</ref><ref>https://mediafugees.com/anne-marie-goumba-dune-guerre-a-lautre</ref>

== Umwuga wa politiki ==
Umugabo we yari amaze igihe kinini avugurura ibya politiki  muri [[Repubulika ya Santara Afurika|Repubulika ya Centrafriqu]]<nowiki/>e, yashinze icyaje guhinduka ishyaka rya Patriotic Front for Progress. Na we yashyigikiye imirimo ya FPP, kandi ahagarara mu matora rusange yo muri [[Repubulika ya Santara Afurika|Repubulika ya Centrafrique]] ya 2005 maze atorerwa kuba umudepite mu karere ka gatanu ka Bangui namajwi 37.32% mu matora yo ku ya 8 Gicurasi. Muri ayo matora , umugabo we ntiyabashije gutsinda. Amaze kujya munteko ishinga amategeko ya [[Repubulika ya Santara Afurika|Repubulika ya Centrafrique]], yatowe nk'uhagarariye [[Repubulika ya Santara Afurika|Repubulika ya Centrafrique]]  mu Nteko ishinga amategeko ya Pan-Afrika<ref name="dictionary" /><ref>https://academicinfluence.com/people/anne-marie-goumba</ref>. Muri Mutarama 2015, yashimye ibikorwa byo kubungabunga amahoro bikorwa n'u [[Rwanda]], avuga ko mu gihe amaze imyaka 30 muri [[Repubulika ya Santara Afurika|Repubulika ya Centrafrique]], atigera yibagirwa ko yavuye mu [[Rwanda]]<ref>http://rwandaises.com/2015/01/rwandais-de-centrafrique-rapatries-au-vu-du-comportement-des-rdf/</ref>. Ni umuhuzabikorwa w’umuryango utegamiye kuri Leta witwa Les Flamboyants, ushaka gukumira ihohoterwa rikorerwa abagore n’abana<ref>http://www.journaldebangui.com/article.php?aid=9559</ref>.

